		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Double Slice",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The paigoel lash out at its foe with both weapons. The paigoel makes two longsword Strikes, each using the paigoel's current multiple attack penalty. Both Strikes must have the same target. The second Strike takes a –2 penalty. If both attacks hit, the paigoel combines their damage, and then add any other applicable effects from both weapons. The paigoel combines the damage from both Strikes and apply resistances and weaknesses only once. This counts as two attacks when calculating the paigoel's multiple attack penalty.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
