		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Storm of Swords",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The paigoel lashes out in a full attack, dealing @Damage[6d6[slashing],6d6[spirit]] damage to all creatures in a @Template[emanation|distance:10], who must attempt at a @Check[reflex|dc:27] save. The paigoel can't use Storm of Swords again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Duration]]{1d4 rounds}. This counts as three attacks when calculating the paigoel's multiple attack penalty.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard} until the start of the paigoel's next turn.</p>",
